<br>
Chanter:  40 to 55 <br>
<br>
Normal thing, tash person first, pet goes after chanter and gets mezed.  If cure poison is not up, i load it quick because that cure tash if you dont know.  Drop tash go after caster.  If im mezzed i med and cast cure poison as soon as unmezzed, then i resist most stuns etc with tash gone.  I do very pretty well against chanters as they have two to contend with.<br>
<br>
Mage:  54 or so<br>
<br>
Send pet after mage, but it seems they have same idea, and the pets end up fighting each other.  One event happend in tene mnts.  She was crafty, and her pet owned my lvl 39 pet at time with ease, and was hard to keep up with her using the hill bug.  No one died but in the half hour fight or so with 2 on each side of battle no one died, just ended up with mobs trained, zone off agro, new pet, nuked healed ect.<br>
