I tried many different strategies and none of the worked.  None of our debuffs or FoL land against anyone who knows that they are in pvp.  Resist gear kills our dueling capability.  If your opponent has no resists be ready for a very easy and very very funny fight.  Slow and blind make for some fun times.<br>
<br>
I could take war's/rogues/monks most of the time but this would entail running in circles as the pet killed them as I had sow.  When they tried to kill the pet I would just heal it.  Going head to head with them didn't really work since with the pet doing crap damage in pvp our damage output just isn't enough...excpet for the rogues.<br>
