<br>
I cant not stress this enough, DO NOT rely on your warder to win a fight for you, that includes you and your warder meleeing like mad. You, Yourself is the one that You must force to do the work, your warder is just there to be annoying and our escape goat.<br>
<br>
When I go off to PK for the night, I don't even use my pet, and if I do, I just SoW &amp; Level buff him to track those damned hill-buggers. I'm sure that PvP is quite different on a bluebie than it is on TZ, VZ, RZ or SZ.. but the basic strategy should be the same.. Don't rely on your pet, use it as a Tool and nothing more.<br>
